Introduction

Serina is a Japanese dancer and singer under 143 Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group MADEIN.

On September 2, 2023, Serina was revealed as a contestant on the survival show "PRODUCE 101 JAPAN THE GIRLS". She was eliminated in the tenth episode, during the third ranking announcement, after placing 21st overall.

On May 10, 2024, Serina was announced as a new member of the girl group MAIDEN under 143 Entertainment.
